high_descs: Turn around and go to the counter with the toaster
Grab the knife off of the counter
Look up at the counter
Slice an apple on the counter
Put the knife on the counter
Grab a slice of apple off the counter
Turn around and go to the microwave
Heat the apple slice in the microwave and then take it out
Turn around and go the fridge
Put the apple slice in the fridge
anns.task_desc: Put a hot apple slice in the fridge

high_descs: Turn right and cross the room to face the toaster.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Look up to face the apple on the counter.
Cut the apple on the counter into three slices.
Place the knife on the right side of the counter.
Pick up the piece of apple on the counter.
Turn around to walk across the room to face the microwave.
Heat the apple piece in the microwave and remove it.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the fridge.
Place the apple piece in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: To heat a piece of apple plus place it in the fridge.

high_descs: turn around, then make a left to face the counter top with the toaster
pick up the knife on the counter top in front of the toaster
lift the knife up and face the toaster on the counter top
slice the onion to the left of the toaster on the counter
place the knife down on the counter top to the right of the toaster
pick up a section of the onion on the counter
go diagonal to the opposite side of the room and face the microwave
place the onion in the microwave for several seconds, then remove it
turn around, then make a diagonal movement to the refrigerator
open the refrigerator door and place the onion on the middle shelf
anns.task_desc: slice an onion, heat it up in the microwave, and cool it down in the refrigerator
